\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When the British won gold in 2021, the Americans finished fifth.\", \"from\": 4660, \"to\": 4724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4669, \"end\": 4676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.8059884532564962, \"rank\": 0.24069269629632678, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Britain was seventh this time.\", \"from\": 4725, \"to\": 4755, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4725, \"end\": 4732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9999786716958493, \"rank\": 2.132870566516481e-05, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The U.S. bumped its total to six golds, one behind leading Australia with four events remaining Sunday.\", \"from\": 4757, \"to\": 4860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4816, \"end\": 4825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.7174861318554714, \"rank\": 0.25399756075804547, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Americans are assured of winning the overall medal count with 25.\", \"from\": 4861, \"to\": 4930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4861, \"end\": 4874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.594349215590107e-27, \"text\": \"The Americans\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Krist\\u00f3f Mil\\u00e1k of Hungary won the men's 100 butterfly, chasing down three swimmers on the return lap.\", \"from\": 4932, \"to\": 5032, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4932, \"end\": 4945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Krist\\u00f3f_Mil\\u00e1k\", \"score\": 0.9999999973315425, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Krist\\u00f3f Mil\\u00e1k\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Krist\\u00f3f_Mil\\u00e1k\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Krist\\u00f3f_Mil\\u00e1k\"}, {\"begin\": 4949, \"end\": 4956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.9995639094383525, \"rank\": 0.00043628081951349005, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mil\\u00e1k was only fourth at the turn, but he rallied to touch in 49.90.\", \"from\": 5034, \"to\": 5102, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Canada grabbed the silver and bronze, with Josh Liendo finishing in 49.99 and Ilya Kharun next at 50.45.\", \"from\": 5103, \"to\": 5207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5103, \"end\": 5109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9932099014677198, \"rank\": 0.005582907064724995, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 5146, \"end\": 5150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9984389787621312, \"rank\": 0.0015115046728740428, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mil\\u00e1k had failed to defend his Olympic title in the 200 butterfly, settling for a silver behind French star Marchand.\", \"from\": 5209, \"to\": 5326, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5305, \"end\": 5311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.715153964433498, \"rank\": 0.3472519821749223, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mil\\u00e1k claimed silver in the 100 fly three years ago, but he did not have to worry about the guy who beat him in that race.\", \"from\": 5328, \"to\": 5450, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"American Caeleb Dressel stunningly failed to qualify for the final, posting only the 13th-fastest time in the semifinals Friday.\", \"from\": 5451, \"to\": 5579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5451, \"end\": 5459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9991125807002037, \"rank\": 0.0008877437961948181, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 5460, \"end\": 5474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caeleb Dressel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kharun added another bronze to the one he garnered in the 200 butterfly.\", \"from\": 5581, \"to\": 5653, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2025 MediaNews Group\", \"from\": 5655, \"to\": 5687, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5672, \"end\": 5687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_First_Media\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"MediaNews Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_First_Media\", \"d